		"description": {
			"value": "<div><p><em>Wondrous Item - Very Rare (Requires Attunement)</em></p></div><p>This candle's magic is activated when the candle is lit.</p><p><strong>Action</strong> - 4 Hours</p><ul><li><p>After burning for 4 hours the candle is destoyed. You can snuff it out early for use at a later time. Deduct the time it burned in increments of 1 minute from its total burn time.</p></li><li><p>While lit, the candle sheds &amp;reference[Dim Light] in a 30 ft radius. While you are within that light, you have &amp;reference[Advantage] on D20 Tests. In addition, a @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class.Item.Z68Q5K5fejrVQZAy]{Cleric} or @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class.Item.653LgVa3sG4ek6b5]{Druid} in the light can cast level 1 spells they have prepared without expending spell slots.</p></li><li><p>Alternatively, when you light the candle for the first time, you can cast <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.sJ4UNpnxQJttNXu9]{Gate}</em> with it. Doing so destroys the candle. The portal created by the spell links to a particular Outer Plane chosen by the GM or determined by rolling on the following table.</p></li></ul><p>@Embed[Compendium.dnd5e.tables24.RollTable.dmgCandleOfInvoc rollable]</p>",
